'''Judlie''' was one of the five massively dug-in strongpoints constructed by the [[Sons and Daughters of Freedom|Freedom's Sons]] around the [[Intergalactic Communications Center]] during the [[Battle of Praesitlyn]]. It was placed as a defense for the rear of [[Zozridor Slayke]]'s forces, six hundred [[Meter/Legends|meters]] behind his command bunker and the army's main defensive position, and benefited from a three-hundred-sixty-degree field of fire. Judlie was the only one of the five redoubts not to be overrun by the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] at any time during the battle.

